to take this one back
to the beginning.

01:28.456 --> 01:30.524
This is where I grew up,

01:30.558 --> 01:33.594
the legendary
Fontainebleau Hotel,

01:33.627 --> 01:36.230
paradise on the sand
in Miami Beach.

01:36.897 --> 01:38.699
It was Dad's.

01:38.732 --> 01:40.534
