from the ground up.

01:41.469 --> 01:44.104
Pretty swank, don't you think?

01:44.138 --> 01:46.407
The Fontainebleau
was the place to see

01:46.440 --> 01:48.409
and be seen.

01:48.442 --> 01:49.943
And it was ours.

01:51.712 --> 01:54.448
Anyone who was anyone
stayed here.

01:54.482 --> 01:57.518
Dad said,
"Build a grand stage,

01:57.551 --> 02:00.521
"and anyone who enters
will play their part."

02:00.554 --> 02:02.256
Sinatra stayed here.

02:02.290 --> 02:03.857
Elvis stayed here.

02:03.891 --> 02:06.460
Freaking James Bond
stayed here.

02:07.595 --> 02:11.732
JFK stayed in suite 1784.

02:13.201 --> 02:17.104
