any excuse to throw a bash.

02:41.629 --> 02:44.298
Dad. Dad. Dad.

02:45.132 --> 02:46.534
Hold on a sec, buddy.

02:46.567 --> 02:49.637
One second, Benny, okay?
The grown-ups are talking.

02:49.670 --> 02:51.905
BEN: And my sixth birthday
was a pretty good one.

02:51.939 --> 02:54.074
Yeah, why don't you
go up to your room,
read some of your comics?

02:54.107 --> 02:56.176
BERNICE: Why don't you
get some of your
birthday cake, honey?

02:56.210 --> 02:58.078
BEN: Hey, my folks had a lot
on their plates.

02:58.111 --> 03:01.882
I mean, who wants
a six-year-old kid
butting in, you know?

03:01.915 --> 03:05.919
I kind of figured
this is where I got
my taste for everything.

03:05.953 --> 03:09.790
I mean, it was right
in front of me,
everywhere, eye high.

03:09.823 --> 03:12.826
