and comic books.

03:17.765 --> 03:20.100
I mean, my life was already
a kind of fantasy

03:20.133 --> 03:22.303
with kings and queens
and movie stars.

03:22.336 --> 03:25.406
So why not add
a superhero into the mix?

03:25.439 --> 03:27.441
Batman was my favorite.

03:28.976 --> 03:30.077
I don't know why.

03:30.110 --> 03:32.713
Maybe it was the lonely,
rich kid thing,

03:32.746 --> 03:34.648
maybe I just liked the car.

03:38.419 --> 03:40.120
WOMAN: Lay 'em down, ladies.

03:40.153 --> 03:44.224
