what do I do with it?
I collect it.

11:26.987 --> 11:30.791
It's actually the second
largest collection of Batman
memorabilia in the world.

11:32.025 --> 11:33.560
Oh, she's cool.

11:34.494 --> 11:36.396
BEN: Catwoman.

11:36.429 --> 11:40.834
Gets her information
from men so she can use it
in her robberies.

11:40.868 --> 11:43.403
