14:46.753 --> 14:48.688
and nobody to play with.

14:51.524 --> 14:56.329
All right, May,
I officially deem
you my first mate,

14:56.363 --> 14:59.599
and your duties include
repelling any invaders,

14:59.632 --> 15:03.336
interlopers, pirates
or other miscreants.

15:18.918 --> 15:21.955
I know that I haven't known
your mom very long,

15:21.989 --> 15:25.592
but I am very serious
about her.

15:27.194 --> 15:28.795
You met her
at a strip club.

15:32.465 --> 15:37.937
Look, why don't you and I make
a bet whether this lasts.

15:37.971 --> 15:41.874
You're, like,
a zillionaire or something.
I don't even get allowance.

15:41.908 --> 15:44.944
Okay, I will bet you

15:44.978 --> 15:48.848
my detective
comic book number 27.

15:48.881 --> 15:50.150
A comic book?

15:50.183 --> 15:52.285
It's Batman's
first appearance.

15:52.319 --> 15:54.021
There's less than 100
in the world.

15:54.054 --> 15:56.123
It's worth about $1 million.

15:57.457 --> 16:02.429
But what do I get
if you lose?

16:02.462 --> 16:05.198
You get my mom.
That's prize enough.

16:05.232 --> 16:06.466
Deal.

