Go, Bubbe.

16:45.538 --> 16:47.840
Narcy.
That's an interesting name.

16:47.874 --> 16:49.142
It's short for Narcisa.

16:49.176 --> 16:52.679
Ah. Narcisa. The dancer.

16:54.547 --> 16:56.049
Lovely. Come in.

16:57.784 --> 17:01.054
