all these pictures?

17:26.579 --> 17:30.383
Well, that used to belong
to us until
Benny's father passed.

17:32.319 --> 17:34.854
Come, you see
that grand piano there?

17:34.887 --> 17:37.124
That was a gift
from Frank Sinatra.

17:38.291 --> 17:39.892
What happened
with your mom?

17:39.926 --> 17:42.495
She's slow to warm up,

17:42.529 --> 17:46.433
and one day,
she's gonna love you
as much as I do.

17:46.466 --> 17:50.002
Come on, you two,
have a look at the pool.
There's a waterfall.

17:52.038 --> 17:55.208
