What is she saying?

18:07.220 --> 18:09.656
She called Bernice a bitch.

18:09.689 --> 18:13.760
All right,
if you don't open the door,
I'm breaking it down.

18:13.793 --> 18:17.297
It's a hollow-core
fiberboard door.
I can bust it with my pinky.

18:17.330 --> 18:21.033
One.
Did you see how that
bitch looked at me, huh?

18:21.067 --> 18:23.270
Where was Batman, huh?

18:23.303 --> 18:26.373
She's like your
Kryptonite or something.

18:26.406 --> 18:29.909
That's Superman.
Batman doesn't care
about Kryptonite.

18:29.942 --> 18:32.545
Two. Look, just open it up.

18:32.579 --> 18:34.814
I have something
very important
I want to tell you.

18:34.847 --> 18:36.916
I don't want
to talk to you.

18:36.949 --> 18:40.052
All right, your landlord
isn't gonna like this. Three.

18:40.086 --> 18:41.087
(BANGING)
Ah!

18:45.725 --> 18:48.261
Narcy, will you marry me?

18:48.295 --> 18:50.330
Or do I need
to break my foot?

18:56.303 --> 18:57.937
What did you say?

18:59.172 --> 19:00.940
Will you marry me, Narcy?

19:03.943 --> 19:05.878
(LAUGHING)

19:12.051 --> 19:13.786
Told you I'd win our bet.

19:24.163 --> 19:26.366
(CROWD CHEERING)

19:33.873 --> 19:36.142
John is already so hammered.

19:36.175 --> 19:38.511
BEN: He had way
too much champagne.

19:38.545 --> 19:40.847
Whoa, no, no.
Thanks again.

19:40.880 --> 19:44.083
I thought a Batman-themed
Bar Mitzvah was tacky,

19:44.116 --> 19:47.153
but this really can't compare.

19:47.186 --> 19:48.955
It was his idea.

19:48.988 --> 19:51.824
Well, we were gonna
have it at the strip club,
but that food is terrible.

19:51.858 --> 19:55.662
Yeah, well,
congratulations to you.

19:55.695 --> 20:00.166
I hope you'll both
be very happy
and have a good lawyer.

20:00.199 --> 20:02.869
Oh, but we do.
They helped us
with the pre-nup.

20:02.902 --> 20:04.170
Her idea.

20:05.171 --> 20:07.540
Well, that's very romantic.

20:08.775 --> 20:11.043
