20:37.236 --> 20:38.671
To the Novacks.

20:41.708 --> 20:45.011
Ben, you remember
my brother Cristobal?

20:45.044 --> 20:46.245
Hey.

20:46.279 --> 20:47.847
You take good care
of my Narcy.

20:53.420 --> 20:55.555
Congratulations.

20:55.588 --> 20:56.789
BEN: And that was that.

20:56.823 --> 20:59.225
Batman married his Catwoman,

20:59.258 --> 21:02.695
and like anything
that's both amazing
and addicting

21:02.729 --> 21:07.634
and possibly very bad
for you, it was great.

21:09.068 --> 21:11.904
Look! This is the one
I was telling you about!

21:12.939 --> 21:15.041
(SPEAKING SPANISH)

21:16.275 --> 21:18.445
Hold it up.
It'll look bigger.

21:18.478 --> 21:20.179
Yeah!

21:20.212 --> 21:25.217
BEN: Years went by,
put May through school.

21:25.251 --> 21:26.953
Maybe I wasn't
the perfect husband,

21:26.986 --> 21:29.656
but I took good care
of the family,

21:29.689 --> 21:32.224
food on the table,
roof over the head.

21:33.259 --> 21:35.395
Everything was good.

21:35.428 --> 21:38.331
We were living
the American dream-ish.

22:03.523 --> 22:04.591
I got to go.

22:42.194 --> 22:44.597
Uh-oh. Look at you!

22:50.102 --> 22:51.170
How was your flight?

22:51.203 --> 22:53.239
(SIGHS) I need to get
a Batplane.

22:54.040 --> 22:55.608
What's this?

